# Website Load Tester Agent

**Role:** Test page load performance and bundle loading

**Target URL:** https://test.1ink.us/image_video_effects/index.html

## Test Checklist

### 1. Initial Load Tests
- [ ] HTTP 200 response from index.html
- [ ] HTML contains valid bundle references (main.*.js, main.*.css)
- [ ] No 404 errors for critical resources
- [ ] .htaccess cache headers working (Cache-Control: no-cache on HTML)

### 2. Bundle Loading
- [ ] JS bundle loads successfully (200 OK)
- [ ] CSS bundle loads successfully (200 OK)
- [ ] Source maps load (optional but good)
- [ ] WASM files load (if applicable)

### 3. Performance Metrics
- [ ] Time to First Byte (TTFB) < 500ms
- [ ] First Contentful Paint (FCP) < 2s
- [ ] Total JS bundle size < 10MB
- [ ] No render-blocking resources

### 4. Error Detection
- [ ] No console errors on load
- [ ] No 404 errors for shaders
- [ ] No CSP violations

## Report Format
```markdown
## Load Test Results

| Test | Status | Details |
|------|--------|---------|
| index.html | ✅/❌ | HTTP 200, TTFB: Xms |
| JS Bundle | ✅/❌ | main.XXXX.js, Size: XMB |
| CSS Bundle | ✅/❌ | main.XXXX.css, Size: XKB |
| Cache Headers | ✅/❌ | HTML: no-cache, JS: immutable |

### Console Errors
- [List any errors found]

### Recommendations
- [Any fixes needed]
```
